{
  "script_id": "calculus",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.14,
      "size": 34272,
      "text": "欢迎来到微积分实验！微积分是数学中最伟大的发明之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.54,
      "size": 40608,
      "text": "它由牛顿和莱布尼茨在17世纪独立发明，彻底改变了我们理解变化的方式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "今天我们将通过可视化，直观地理解导数和积分的几何意义。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "derivative-concept",
      "line_id": "derivative-concept-1",
      "filename": "derivative-concept-derivative-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/derivative-concept-derivative-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.66,
      "size": 26496,
      "text": "导数描述的是函数在某一点的瞬时变化率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "derivative-concept",
      "line_id": "derivative-concept-2",
      "filename": "derivative-concept-derivative-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/derivative-concept-derivative-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "想象你在开车，速度表显示的就是位置对时间的导数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "derivative-concept",
      "line_id": "derivative-concept-3",
      "filename": "derivative-concept-derivative-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/derivative-concept-derivative-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "在图形上，导数等于函数曲线在该点的切线斜率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "derivative-concept",
      "line_id": "derivative-concept-4",
      "filename": "derivative-concept-derivative-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/derivative-concept-derivative-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "斜率为正表示函数在增加，斜率为负表示函数在减少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "tangent-line",
      "line_id": "tangent-line-1",
      "filename": "tangent-line-tangent-line-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/tangent-line-tangent-line-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.4,
      "size": 22464,
      "text": "图中蓝色曲线是我们要研究的函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "tangent-line",
      "line_id": "tangent-line-2",
      "filename": "tangent-line-tangent-line-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/tangent-line-tangent-line-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "红色的直线是在某一点的切线，它刚好贴着曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "tangent-line",
      "line_id": "tangent-line-3",
      "filename": "tangent-line-tangent-line-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/tangent-line-tangent-line-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "拖动滑块改变x的位置，观察切线如何随之变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "tangent-line",
      "line_id": "tangent-line-4",
      "filename": "tangent-line-tangent-line-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/tangent-line-tangent-line-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.65,
      "size": 42480,
      "text": "注意切线的斜率：在曲线上升的地方斜率为正，下降的地方斜率为负。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "derivative-formula",
      "line_id": "derivative-formula-1",
      "filename": "derivative-formula-derivative-formula-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/derivative-formula-derivative-formula-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.87,
      "size": 61920,
      "text": "导数的定义是极限：f撇x等于h趋近于0时，f(x+h)减f(x)除以h的极限。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "derivative-formula",
      "line_id": "derivative-formula-2",
      "filename": "derivative-formula-derivative-formula-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/derivative-formula-derivative-formula-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "这个极限描述的是割线斜率趋近于切线斜率的过程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "derivative-formula",
      "line_id": "derivative-formula-3",
      "filename": "derivative-formula-derivative-formula-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/derivative-formula-derivative-formula-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "常见的导数公式：x的n次方的导数是n乘以x的n-1次方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "derivative-formula",
      "line_id": "derivative-formula-4",
      "filename": "derivative-formula-derivative-formula-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/derivative-formula-derivative-formula-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.57,
      "size": 41184,
      "text": "例如，x平方的导数是2x，x立方的导数是3x平方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "integral-concept",
      "line_id": "integral-concept-1",
      "filename": "integral-concept-integral-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/integral-concept-integral-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "现在让我们来看积分。积分可以理解为累加的过程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "integral-concept",
      "line_id": "integral-concept-2",
      "filename": "integral-concept-integral-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/integral-concept-integral-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "定积分的几何意义是曲线与x轴之间的面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "integral-concept",
      "line_id": "integral-concept-3",
      "filename": "integral-concept-integral-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/integral-concept-integral-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "如果曲线在x轴上方，面积为正；在x轴下方，面积为负。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "integral-concept",
      "line_id": "integral-concept-4",
      "filename": "integral-concept-integral-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/integral-concept-integral-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "积分符号像一个拉长的S，代表求和的意思。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "area-demo",
      "line_id": "area-demo-1",
      "filename": "area-demo-area-demo-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/area-demo-area-demo-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.83,
      "size": 29232,
      "text": "图中阴影部分就是定积分的值——曲线下的面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "area-demo",
      "line_id": "area-demo-2",
      "filename": "area-demo-area-demo-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/area-demo-area-demo-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "调整积分的上下限，观察面积如何变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "area-demo",
      "line_id": "area-demo-3",
      "filename": "area-demo-area-demo-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/area-demo-area-demo-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "我们可以用很多小矩形来近似这个面积，这就是黎曼和的思想。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "area-demo",
      "line_id": "area-demo-4",
      "filename": "area-demo-area-demo-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/area-demo-area-demo-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "矩形越多越细，近似就越精确，极限就是精确的积分值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "ftc",
      "line_id": "ftc-1",
      "filename": "ftc-ftc-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/ftc-ftc-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "微积分最重要的发现是：导数和积分是互逆运算！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "ftc",
      "line_id": "ftc-2",
      "filename": "ftc-ftc-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/ftc-ftc-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "这就是微积分基本定理，它连接了微分和积分两个看似不同的概念。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "ftc",
      "line_id": "ftc-3",
      "filename": "ftc-ftc-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/ftc-ftc-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.0,
      "size": 47952,
      "text": "如果F是f的原函数，那么f从a到b的定积分等于F(b)减F(a)。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "ftc",
      "line_id": "ftc-4",
      "filename": "ftc-ftc-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/ftc-ftc-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "这个定理让我们可以用求原函数的方法来计算定积分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-1",
      "filename": "applications-applications-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/applications-applications-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.25,
      "size": 20016,
      "text": "微积分在现实中有广泛的应用。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-2",
      "filename": "applications-applications-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/applications-applications-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "物理学中，速度是位置的导数，加速度是速度的导数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-3",
      "filename": "applications-applications-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/applications-applications-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "经济学中，边际成本是总成本对产量的导数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-4",
      "filename": "applications-applications-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/applications-applications-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "工程学中，积分用于计算不规则形状的面积和体积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-1",
      "filename": "summary-summary-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/summary-summary-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.25,
      "size": 20016,
      "text": "让我们总结一下今天学到的内容。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-2",
      "filename": "summary-summary-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/summary-summary-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.78,
      "size": 28512,
      "text": "导数描述瞬时变化率，几何上是切线斜率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-3",
      "filename": "summary-summary-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/summary-summary-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "积分描述累积量，几何上是曲线下面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-4",
      "filename": "summary-summary-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/summary-summary-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "微积分基本定理告诉我们，导数和积分是互逆运算。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "calculus",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-5",
      "filename": "summary-summary-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/calculus/yunxi/summary-summary-5.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "希望通过这个实验，你对微积分有了更直观的理解！"
    }
  ],
